{
  "stem": "1873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 306.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was divided in two phases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The first phase, which should last from 4:00 to 5:00, was the killing of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Killing them quietly, without arousing any suspicion, with knives and axes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The second phase was that after killing, when we assemble for the roll call, we should explode and have an open revolt and use the guns we'd needed to get from the killed Germans.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How to kill the Germans?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From now, from the perspective, I think it was very easy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the Germans depend on the guards on the towers, on the Ukrainian guards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, themselves, were the staff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the sorting place, where we were sorting, there was always a German, [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wolf ?] was his name, who didn't supervise we shouldn't escape, he supervised we should walk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so on in other places too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but they weren't obligated, like the guards in the towers to stay on the spot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could go grab a cup of coffee, they could go away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if he killed one Nazi supervising the, the sorting of the shoes, then another Nazi who passed by, he didn't see him, he wasn't alarmed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and everything was running smooth with the Kapos, the Kapos that run everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The regular flow was like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Five would let you finish the work, the Kapo whistled the whistle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we assembled in groups, and we would march to the main yard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, we go to the kitchen to pick up our food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And 5:30, a half an hour later, after they eat, was the roll call.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That time-- this was the dangerous time-- because at that point in the role call, all Germans must come assemble and they count us.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
